<subSubSection id="61C672C9A736B237696830F74153C87C" pageId="6" pageNumber="45" type="host">
<paragraph id="23CCCF19765609E7181F5DAF4AF140C5" pageId="6" pageNumber="45">Relation to the host plant.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3036DD7B4B7B5CF2CE0DC58EA8B5DCE9" pageId="6" pageNumber="45">The mites inhabit the under surface of leaves as vagrants without showing symptoms of damage to the host plant.</paragraph>
